'''Loharani''' ({{Lang-bal|لوہارانی}}) is a [[Baloch people|Baloch]] tribe in [[Sibi District]] of [[Balochistan (Pakistan)|Balochistan]], [[Pakistan]]. The Loharani are one of four Baloch clans.

